  "body": "### Overview\r\nImprove the method to increase the nonce for an unlocked account to a desired value.\r\n\r\nUse case: Deploy a contract at a specific address (calculated from sender address and nonce).\r\n\r\nCurrently we have to loop empty transactions which creates a lot of spam in the console (each tx is printed).\r\n\r\n### Specification\r\nNaive: I added a PR with an example on how to implement it. \r\nBetter: Ganache support to increase nonce. [See here.](https://github.com/trufflesuite/ganache-cli/issues/736)\r\nAlternative 1: Implement a batch transaction method where we can pass a list of transactions and get a list of receipts back, executing the transactions silently.\r\nAlternative 2: Add a silent argument to the transaction method.\r\n\r\n### Dependencies\r\nMaybe https://github.com/trufflesuite/ganache-cli/issues/736\r\n",
